folder: Seguine Avenue & Johnston Terrace, Staten Island, NY
text:
(1)

Seguine Avenue, east side, between Johnston Terrace and Princes Bay, showing the S.S. White Dental Works. The view is southeastward from Johnston Terrace.

September 7, 1936

(2)

September 7, 1936

(3)

The north wing of the S.S. White factory, seen from Seguine Avenue, at Purdy Place.
